FBIS4-52485 "dreas091_a_94011" FBIS-EAS-94-091 Daily Report 11 May 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Commercial Banks To Open More Offices in SRV Commercial Banks To Open More Offices in SRV OW1105104294 Tokyo KYODO in English 1029 GMT 11 May 94 OW1105104294 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, May 11 KYODO -- Major Japanese commercial banks Mitsubishi Bank and Sanwa Bank will open representative offices in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam, on Thursday [12 May], bank officials said Wednesday. The offices, each staffed by three officials, will collect information on the Vietnamese economy as the country shifts to a market economy, the officials said. The opening of the offices will bring to seven the number of Japanese banks which have representative offices in Vietnam.
